{"tid":1921643,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Cajon問題 - 有冇高手解答","createTime":"2020-03-12T05:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:07:56.000Z","uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e8bdddf378fceafb75dd8326339f0c1c800b3b","tid":1921643,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"2016年2月喺深水埗深之都買咗個cajon<br />\n好似$800-1000左右<br />\n唔記得了 太耐<br />\n<br />\n其間隔咗2年3年冇打 <br />\n拎返出嚟 發現啲聲好柒 唔知當初點解會買 但當初好似冇咁柒<br />\n我有諗過係咪潮濕問題 有諗過係咪螺絲鬆緊問題 但發現都唔太關事 我又有試過tune鬆tune緊 好似唔係好識tune 同埋就算tune 好似係關個鼓本身事<br />\n<br />\n我個cajon入面係4線 V V 咁樣嘅構造 我睇其他有啲係一排snare弦咁 我唔知係咪我內線有啲簡陋？同埋我入面又冇鈴鈴 <br />\n<br />\n我最近同朋友出去busking 個cajon bass snare同hi hat好似分唔開咁 hi hat snare啲聲又散 bass又唔重 <br />\n好想換個新/我呢個有冇得救？<br />\n<br />\n出面睇好多人介紹standcajon? 590? 550? <br />\n大概幾錢到 如果我$1000-1800 budget <br />\n有冇介紹？ 起碼聲要正常 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8tsBF5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tsBF5P.jpg&h=c8a80ade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20f43862897371315524cd384940bd147f6d5b05","tid":1921643,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"屌好似開錯台？"},{"pid":"a17e187e9dfcf51e61a7cc07d77a7bc004eba459","tid":1921643,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"聽日再開過 喺樂器台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72233a3ec7f11a898f678e0b4c968c7c57ecba47","tid":1921643,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"平賣個靚cajon比你"},{"pid":"f494c51814ccb7e312b3180639ee6645f107570d","tid":1921643,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72233a3ec7f11a898f678e0b4c968c7c57ecba47","tid":1921643,"uid":50122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"202